plot: It's a party in the kitchen each and every afternoon, as &"The Chew&" celebrates and explores life through food. Each show brings viewers smart and intelligent talk that engages the audience in a daily dose of food, life and fun with conversations about everything from cooking, holidays and home entertaining to trends like food trucks and urban gardens.   Written by  ABC Publicity
